## Routing & tenancy (core-fe)

When you change any matched file:

1. **Read** `agent-os/skills/routing-tenancy/SKILL.md`.
2. **Scaffold** new URL segments with `route-island` first — this rule covers guards and gateway only.
3. **Protected routes** — use `gatewayFromManifest(manifest)` when the island declares `permission` / `module`.
4. **Org slug chain** — follow `src/app/guards/GUARDS.OVERVIEW.md` order; unknown org → 404, never leak existence.
5. **Session** — reuse `hydrateSessionContext` / `invalidateSessionContext`; do not fork `me/context` fetch paths.
6. **Tests** — update `tests/security/route-access-matrix.security.test.ts` when access policy changes.

See **`docs/reference/routing-and-tenancy.md`** and **`docs/reference/frontend-platform.md`**.
